    "pageTitle": "Privacy Policy",
    "content": "Synedria collects and processes personal data in compliance with the European Regulation 2016/679 (GDPR). Collected data (name, email, avatar via OAuth provider, city, availability, skills) is used exclusively for the platform's operation. Data is not shared with third parties. You can request deletion of your account and all associated data at any time from your profile page. For privacy-related questions, contact us through the contact page."
  },
